{"tid":761649,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"隊長特權？拉莫斯又遲歸隊","createTime":"2018-07-30T14:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T16:15:31.000Z","uid":20634,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6f7cfbfd79bb641b30c12e30fa7b784d5595ec","tid":761649,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=rOai4qxVptJ7VVmcqwObHdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=a844c6a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里大軍已抵達邁阿密，預備周三對曼聯的國際冠軍盃賽事，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">隊長</span>沙治奧拉莫斯就<span style=\"color: red;\">多唞幾日</span>，周二才會歸隊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界盃完結已經兩周，世盃後獲准休假的球員，不少已返回所屬球會操練。皇馬方面，基羅拿華斯、丹尼爾卡華積、沙治奧拉莫斯（Sergio Ramos）均選擇世盃後在美國度假，而拿華斯、卡華積周六已經與大軍會合，<span style=\"color: red;\">唯有拉莫斯仍在享受假期</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，日前他就在社交媒體上載自己釣魚的相片。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，拿祖費南迪斯、馬高阿辛斯奧、盧卡斯華斯基斯、艾斯高等狂牛國腳較早時間已經歸隊，現時只剩拉莫斯一人。<span style=\"color: red;\">這似乎是皇馬慣例，去年夏天西班牙在國際賽對馬其頓之後，拉莫斯亦比其他隊友遲幾天向皇馬報到。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，拉莫斯似乎準備就緒，最新在社交媒體上發放自己一邊聽著Marc Anthony的歌曲、一邊在跑步機上操練的短片。"},{"pid":"31515fd7204f0c304c4d6fe78f5bf4c08448a8a1","tid":761649,"uid":161311,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"猁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f85eb675a1e6ff0153dcbb2468df38a6324f42c","tid":761649,"uid":192678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"又怨"},{"pid":"3407299b87ae4923cc47bba47f54a340d6f9c819","tid":761649,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1023935291923619840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r